entry.title: The Youngest Head Coach in European Soccer Is 30 Years Old---and Nearly Undefeated
entry.content: Stade de Reims coach Will Still has lost just once in the French league this season. His lack of pro certifications mean the club pays a €25,000 fine every match.

entry.title: Ukraine Says Bakhmut Tactics Will Give It Advantages Elsewhere
entry.content: Kyiv’s efforts to exhaust and deplete Russian forces in the eastern city will help it reclaim other territory in the country, a Ukrainian commander said.

entry.title: The Jobs Most Exposed to ChatGPT
entry.content: A new study finds that AI tools could more quickly handle at least half of the tasks that auditors, interpreters and writers do now.
